text: Scott Moe (born July 31, 1973) is a Canadian politician. He is the 15th and current Premier of Saskatchewan, in office since February 2018. He is a member of the Legislative Assembly of Saskatchewan for the riding of Rosthern- Shellbrook. He was Minister of the Environment from 2016 to 2017, after which he resigned to launch his campaign for the leadership of the Saskatchewan Party. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1973 births Category:Premiers of Saskatchewan
